      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong claim. My procurement lead is being pretty skeptical though—he's seen other brands in this class die around the 16 or 18-hour mark when the load is consistent. Do you have any specific test data or technical documentation that backs up that 24-hour continuous heavy-use claim? I need something concrete to show him so we can move forward with the signature today.",
